content.rendered:
Directed by Raama Mehra

Written by Raama Mehra

Cast Vikas Anand. Shilpa Gandhi (Soniya mother). Adi Irani (K k sawant). Pradeep Kabra (Rajan). Rizwan Kalshyan (Iqubal Cikna). Shahbaaz Khan (Salim sultan). Abhishek Khanna (Bajrangi). Kiran Kumar (Manti somnath). Pakhi Mendola (Child soniya).Anil Nagrath. Sagarika Neha (Soniya). Laxman Singh Rajput (Manmohan). Vishnu Dhanraj Sharma (Khanna shab). Vivek Kumar Singh (Abhishak khanna’s Friend (as Vivak Kumar Singh)). Jai Yadav (Acp vijay)

Languages Hindi

Producers Laxman Singh Rajput. Mahesh Sharma. Vishnu Dhanraj Sharma

Production Rama Dhanraj Production
